data.description: Step into a modern haven with updated LVP floors that gracefully traverse this home, leading to a culinary delight in the kitchen boasting granite countertops and a stylish tile backsplash. Entertain effortlessly in the backyard oasis featuring a welcoming fire pit within the fenced in backyard, offering privacy and serenity. This home is nestled in a vibrant neighborhood, conveniently situated near schools, providing easy accessibility for residents. Discover a spacious primary bedroom with a coveted walk-in closet, ensuring ample storage space for your most important attire. Enjoy the airy ambiance of the open-concept design creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation and gatherings. Experience the perfect blend of comfort and contemporary living in this exquisite property.
